  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"B2-OQWU8\">①如果没有疫苗和药物可控制这种病原体</p><p data-pid=\"sHcNVvBA\">性别一栏会被作废。</p><p data-pid=\"MluYqcAM\">根据瘟疫公司规则，两种病原体之间通常会共存。假设这句话成立，各种病原体之间是相互独立的。</p><p data-pid=\"vF1p-oVY\">现有一位已经完工的天赋党小姐姐和类似的小哥哥，我们不可能分辨出他们的t身份。随着传播进程展开，精神耐受力弱的人将因并发症【抑郁】而亡，剩下的人由于<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=75528473&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=4&amp;q=%E7%97%85%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">病原体<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>轮番感染而成为GenderFluid.</p><p data-pid=\"2MOGD1EM\">触发社会大讨论，然后性别作为法律上确定一个人的特征正式作废。不久后疫情幸存者都想开了，于是终止了所有<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=75528473&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E9%87%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">性别重置手术<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。</p><p data-pid=\"OOt6RHcv\">由于普遍的Gender Fluid并不能改变人类<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=75528473&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%9C%89%E6%80%A7%E7%94%9F%E6%AE%96&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">有性生殖<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>的底子，这个世界线上人类的繁殖方式将与目前的伦理道德完全冲突，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=75528473&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E9%A1%BA%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">顺性别<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>状态人士被迫全部或大部分卷入有偿性市场。婚姻制度彻底被消灭，家庭概念也将消失。</p><p data-pid=\"gv4VZ9vH\">最后，概括的讲，就是生育率将低的可怕。假使<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=75528473&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%B7%A8%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">跨性别<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>病原体的传染并不过多的影响人类的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=75528473&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%A0%91&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">科技树<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，则最终结果如下，人类的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=75528473&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=K%E5%80%BC&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">K值<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>将比现在的人口数量低好几个数量级，但是人均生产值和资源可能会高的离谱。当然，实际的GD会严重折损人的生产力，因此相较来说人类灭绝的可能性仍然高到不可忽视的程度。</p><p data-pid=\"lbFjE21g\">②如果疫情被疫苗或药物控制了</p><p data-pid=\"FAr-91Zk\">不出1年，性别认同障碍作为一项<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=75528473&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">病理症状<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>将永久的消失。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
